main event: The witness claims to have taken photographs of a UFO over Wreck Pond in Spring Lake, New Jersey on February 20, 1965.
interesting points: The witness states that the object was also visible to the naked eye.
The witness passed the photographs to Air Force Intelligence for analysis.
Air Force Intelligence was unable to process or submit the negatives for further investigation.
The photographs were returned to the witness.
The report concludes that there was 'INSUFFICIENT DATA FOR EVALUATION' due to the lack of photographs or negatives.
photographs: yes, but not available for analysis
